{"published time": "2024-03-06T23-55-00-00-00", "images": ["https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/albacete.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/albacete.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/8.Marz2024_Leipzig-2.cleaned-1024x794.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/8.Marz2024_Leipzig-4.cleaned-768x1024.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Koln1-1024x768.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Altendorf1-1024x768.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Altendorf2-1024x768.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Hamburg-8March-Posters.jpg", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Denmark.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Trondheim_1.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Trondheim_2.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Trondheim_3.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Trondheim_7.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Trondheim_8-1024x682.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Trondheim_9-1024x682.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Trondheim_11-1024x682.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Trondheim_13.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Finland_Poster.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Finland_1.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Finland_2.webp"], "content": "<div class=\"post-thumbnail\">\n <img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" height=\"768\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/albacete.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/albacete.webp\" width=\"1024\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\n <p>\n  We share an overview of actions and statements that we have seen for the 8\n  <sup>\n   th\n  </sup>\n  March this year.\n </p>\n <p>\n  Regarding Turkey we have already shared a\n  <a href=\"https://redherald.org/2024/03/04/turkey-activities-and-statement-for-the-8th-of-march/\">\n   statement\n  </a>\n  by the New Democratic Women (YDK) as well as activities carried out by them in Istanbul. We have also shared a\n  <a href=\"https://redherald.org/2024/03/03/turkey-call-for-the-8th-of-march/\">\n   statement\n  </a>\n  by the Purple-Red collective. YDK has also published a poster and put up dazibaos mobilizing for the 8\n  <sup>\n   th\n  </sup>\n  of March in Izmir.\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter\">\n  <div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n   <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-dnt=\"true\" data-width=\"550\">\n    <p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"tr\">\n     We are in Izmir Alsancak on 8 March International Working Women's Day!\n     <br/>\n     <br/>\n     Saylan Saylan Cultural Center\n     <br/>\n     \ud83d\udcc68 Mart\n     <br/>\n     \ud83d\udd5518.00\n     <a href=\"https://t.co/n8xrRmF7GH\">\n      pic.twitter.com/n8xrRmF7GH\n     </a>\n    </p>\n    - New Democrat Woman (@ydkresmi)\n    <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ydkresmi/status/1765356637924081783?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n     March 6, 2024\n    </a>\n   </blockquote>\n   <script async=\"\" charset=\"utf-8\" src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\">\n   </script>\n  </div>\n </figure>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter\">\n  <div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n   <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-dnt=\"true\" data-width=\"550\">\n    <p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"tr\">\n     We are on the streets of Izmir with our wall newspapers.\n     <br/>\n     <br/>\n     We meet in Izmir Alsancak on March 8, World Working Women's Day, and you come!\n     <br/>\n     <br/>\n     \ud83d\udccdalsancak T\u00fcrkan Saylan Cultural Center\n     <br/>\n     \ud83d\udcc58 March Friday\n     <br/>\n     \ud83d\udd5518.00\n     <a href=\"https://t.co/Sm1oTnniVw\">\n      pic.twitter.com/Sm1oTnniVw\n     </a>\n    </p>\n    - New Democrat Woman (@ydkresmi)\n    <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ydkresmi/status/1764954703807365169?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n     March 5, 2024\n    </a>\n   </blockquote>\n   <script async=\"\" charset=\"utf-8\" src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\">\n   </script>\n  </div>\n </figure>\n <p>\n  In Brazil, the People\u2019s Woman\u2019s Movement (MFP) have published a\n  <a href=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/movimento-feminino-popular-lanca-boletim-para-8-de-marco-de-2024/\">\n   Bulletin\n  </a>\n  for the 8\n  <sup>\n   th\n  </sup>\n  of March. We have recently published an\n  <a href=\"https://redherald.org/2024/03/04/brazil-the-inextinguishable-flame-of-the-battle-of-stalingrad/\">\n   article\n  </a>\n  by the MFP on the victory of the Red Army in the battle of Stalingrad, with a particular focus on the heroic struggle of women.\n </p>\n <p>\n  In Lyon, France, the People\u2019s Women\u2019s Committee has called for a meeting on the 7\n  <sup>\n   th\n  </sup>\n  of March.\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter\">\n  <div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n   <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-dnt=\"true\" data-width=\"550\">\n    <p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"fr\">\n     \ud83d\udccdLyon\n     <br/>\n     Come this Thursday, March 7, 6 p.m. on the PDA H109 Campus for the March 8 meeting of the Popular Women's Committee!\n     <a href=\"https://t.co/pNdMWtSjEj\">\n      pic.twitter.com/pNdMWtSjEj\n     </a>\n    </p>\n    - Revolutionary Youth League (@Liguej_R)\n    <a href=\"https://twitter.com/LigueJ_R/status/1765331826443260390?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n     March 6, 2024\n    </a>\n   </blockquote>\n   <script async=\"\" charset=\"utf-8\" src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\">\n   </script>\n  </div>\n </figure>\n <p>\n  In the Spanish State, the newspaper Servir al Pueblo has published an editorial, which we have already translated to English, on how the State and imperialism sustain patriarchal violence.\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-the-red-herald wp-block-embed-the-red-herald\">\n  <div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n   <blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"KEipB6XDfq\">\n    <a href=\"https://redherald.org/2024/03/03/spanish-state-servir-al-pueblo-the-state-and-imperialism-sustain-patriarchal-violence/\">\n     Spanish State \u2013 Servir al Pueblo: The State and imperialism sustain patriarchal violence\n    </a>\n   </blockquote>\n   <iframe class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"KEipB6XDfq\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"338\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" scrolling=\"no\" security=\"restricted\" src=\"https://redherald.org/2024/03/03/spanish-state-servir-al-pueblo-the-state-and-imperialism-sustain-patriarchal-violence/embed/#?secret=Y60Vp1e6tC#?secret=KEipB6XDfq\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" title=\"\u201cSpanish State \u2013 Servir al Pueblo: The State and imperialism sustain patriarchal violence\u201d \u2014 The Red Herald\" width=\"600\">\n   </iframe>\n  </div>\n </figure>\n <p>\n  Servier Al Pueblo Has also published in Translation into Spanish of A\n  <a href=\"https://serviralpuebloperiodico.wordpress.com/2024/02/28/aurora-picornell-simbolo-de-mujer-comunista/\">\n   document\n  </a>\n  by the MFP of Brazil, on the life and work of Aurora Picornell.\n </p>\n <p>\n  Also a graffiti has been made in\n  <a href=\"https://serviralpuebloperiodico.wordpress.com/2024/03/06/albacete-pintada-por-la-mujer-combatiente-palestina/\">\n   Albacete\n  </a>\n  , with the slogan \u201cLong Live the Palestinian woman with a rifle in the hand!\u201d\n </p>\n <div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n  <figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9574\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"768\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/albacete.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/albacete.webp\" width=\"1024\"/>\n   <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">\n    Graffiti in Albacete, Spanish State. Source: Serve at the pueblo\n   </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n </div>\n <p>\n  In Austria, red flag Has\n  <a href=\"https://www.rotefahne.at/post/heraus-zum-8-m%C3%A4rz-dem-internationalen-kampftag-der-frauen\">\n   called for demonstrations\n  </a>\n  on the 8\n  <sup>\n   th\n  </sup>\n  of March in the cities of Wien, Linz and Innsbruck. We have previously published a translation of an article by Rote Fahne on the struggle for the oldest self-managed autonomous women\u2019s center in Europe\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-the-red-herald wp-block-embed-the-red-herald\">\n  <div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n   <blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"NC45A4Y2hC\">\n    <a href=\"https://redherald.org/2024/03/02/austria-fz-stays-the-struggle-for-the-oldest-self-managed-autonomous-womens-center-in-europe-continues/\">\n     Austria \u2013 FZ stays! \u2013 The struggle for the oldest self-managed autonomous women\u2019s center in Europe continues!\n    </a>\n   </blockquote>\n   <iframe class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"NC45A4Y2hC\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"338\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" scrolling=\"no\" security=\"restricted\" src=\"https://redherald.org/2024/03/02/austria-fz-stays-the-struggle-for-the-oldest-self-managed-autonomous-womens-center-in-europe-continues/embed/#?secret=y2zKm5KzLb#?secret=NC45A4Y2hC\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" title=\"\u201cAustria \u2013 FZ stays! \u2013 The struggle for the oldest self-managed autonomous women\u2019s center in Europe continues!\u201d \u2014 The Red Herald\" width=\"600\">\n   </iframe>\n  </div>\n </figure>\n <p>\n  From Germany we have published a translation of a call for the 8\n  <sup>\n   th\n  </sup>\n  of March by the Red Women\u2019s Committees\n  <em>\n   .\n  </em>\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-the-red-herald wp-block-embed-the-red-herald\">\n  <div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n   <blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"wU5xghaTKn\">\n    <a href=\"https://redherald.org/2024/03/03/germany-call-for-8th-of-march/\">\n     Germany: Call for 8th of March\n    </a>\n   </blockquote>\n   <iframe class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"wU5xghaTKn\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"338\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" scrolling=\"no\" security=\"restricted\" src=\"https://redherald.org/2024/03/03/germany-call-for-8th-of-march/embed/#?secret=2KB9wdvX2V#?secret=wU5xghaTKn\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" title=\"\u201cGermany: Call for 8th of March\u201d \u2014 The Red Herald\" width=\"600\">\n   </iframe>\n  </div>\n </figure>\n <p>\n  <em>\n   Several events have also been called for in different cities in Germany. Earlier this month there has been presentations in\n   <a href=\"https://demvolkedienen.org/index.php/de/t-brd/8345-bremen-bremerhaven-veranstaltungen-und-demonstration-zum-internationalen-frauenkampftag\">\n    Bremen\n   </a>\n   ,\n   <a href=\"https://demvolkedienen.org/index.php/de/t-proletarischer-feminismus/8348-nrw-mobilisierung-zum-8-maerz-2024\">\n    Cologne and Bochum\n   </a>\n   . On the 7\n  </em>\n  <em>\n   <sup>\n    th\n   </sup>\n  </em>\n  <em>\n   of March there will be an event by the Red Women\u2019s Committee in Hamburg. On the 8\n  </em>\n  <em>\n   <sup>\n    th\n   </sup>\n  </em>\n  <em>\n   of March the Red Women\u2019s Committee has called for demonstrations in\n   <a href=\"https://demvolkedienen.org/index.php/de/t-proletarischer-feminismus/8335-leipzig-mobilisierung-zum-8-maerz-2024\">\n    Leipzig\n   </a>\n   ,\n   <a href=\"https://demvolkedienen.org/index.php/de/t-brd/8345-bremen-bremerhaven-veranstaltungen-und-demonstration-zum-internationalen-frauenkampftag\">\n    Bremerhaven\n   </a>\n   ,\n   <a href=\"https://demvolkedienen.org/index.php/de/t-proletarischer-feminismus/8348-nrw-mobilisierung-zum-8-maerz-2024\">\n    Essen and Cologne\n   </a>\n   . There has also been reports of mobilization for the events:\n  </em>\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-gallery aligncenter has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-1 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9556\" data-id=\"9556\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"794\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/8.Marz2024_Leipzig-2.cleaned-1024x794.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/8.Marz2024_Leipzig-2.cleaned-1024x794.webp\" width=\"1024\"/>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9557\" data-id=\"9557\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1024\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/8.Marz2024_Leipzig-4.cleaned-768x1024.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/8.Marz2024_Leipzig-4.cleaned-768x1024.webp\" width=\"768\"/>\n  </figure>\n  <figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-caption wp-element-caption\">\n   <em>\n    Posters mobilizing for the 8\n    <sup>\n     th\n    </sup>\n    of March in Leipzig. Source: serve the people\n   </em>\n  </figcaption>\n </figure>\n <div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n  <figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9565\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"768\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Koln1-1024x768.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Koln1-1024x768.webp\" width=\"1024\"/>\n   <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">\n    <em>\n     Posters mobilizing for the 8\n     <sup>\n      th\n     </sup>\n     of March in Cologne. Source: serve the people\n    </em>\n   </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n </div>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-gallery aligncenter has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-2 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9558\" data-id=\"9558\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"768\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Altendorf1-1024x768.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Altendorf1-1024x768.webp\" width=\"1024\"/>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9559\" data-id=\"9559\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"768\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Altendorf2-1024x768.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Altendorf2-1024x768.webp\" width=\"1024\"/>\n  </figure>\n  <figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-caption wp-element-caption\">\n   <em>\n    Posters mobilizing for the 8\n    <sup>\n     th\n    </sup>\n    of March in Essen. Source: serve the people\n   </em>\n  </figcaption>\n </figure>\n <div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n  <figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9564\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"516\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 906px) 100vw, 906px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Hamburg-8March-Posters.jpg\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Hamburg-8March-Posters.jpg\" width=\"906\"/>\n   <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">\n    <em>\n     Posters mobilizing for the 8\n     <sup>\n      th\n     </sup>\n     of March in Hamburg. Source: serve the people\n    </em>\n   </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n </div>\n <p>\n  In Italy, The News Site for popular democracy Has Published a\n  <a href=\"https://www.perlademocraziapopolare.com/per-un-otto-marzo-internazionalista-contro-il-fascismo-e-limperialismo/\">\n   flyer\n  </a>\n  for an internationalist 8\n  <sup>\n   th\n  </sup>\n  of March against fascism and imperialism.\n </p>\n <p>\n  <em>\n   We have previously\n   <a href=\"https://redherald.org/2024/03/02/some-actions-for-the-8th-of-march-in-the-nordic-countries/\">\n    reported\n   </a>\n   on actions for the 8th of March in Denmark, Norway and Finland. There are now reports of more actions in the Nordic countries.\n  </em>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <em>\n   In Copenhagen, Denmark,\n   <a href=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.wordpress.com/2024/03/06/kobenhavn-dazibaos-for-mobilisering-til-8-marts/\">\n    On the poster\n   </a>\n   with the slogans \u201cOut on the streets March 8!\u201d, \u201cAgainst imperialism and patriarchy!\u201d and \u201cFor a red class line in the women\u2019s movement!\u201d have been put up in proletarian neighborhoods.\n  </em>\n </p>\n <div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n  <figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9560\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"512\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Denmark.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Denmark.webp\" width=\"768\"/>\n   <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">\n    <em>\n     Dazibao mobilizing for the 8\n     <sup>\n      th\n     </sup>\n     of March in Copenhagen, Denmark. Source: Socialistisk Revolution\n    </em>\n   </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n </div>\n <p>\n  <em>\n   In Norway, Kampkomiteen has published a\n   <a href=\"https://kampkomiteen.net/?p=6913\">\n    call\n   </a>\n   for the 8\n  </em>\n  <em>\n   <sup>\n    th\n   </sup>\n  </em>\n  <em>\n   of March, with events and demonstrations in the cities off Oslo, Bergen, Trondheim and Kristiansand. There are also several reports of posters being put up in the Region of\n   <a href=\"https://kampkomiteen.net/?p=6934\">\n    Tr\u00f8ndelag\n   </a>\n   . The posters mobilizing for the 8\n  </em>\n  <em>\n   <sup>\n    th\n   </sup>\n  </em>\n  <em>\n   of March were put up in the regional capital,\n   <a href=\"https://kampkomiteen.net/?p=6890\">\n    Trondheim\n   </a>\n   , as well as several other places. You can read more reports\n   <a href=\"https://kampkomiteen.net/?p=6902\">\n    here\n   </a>\n   and\n   <a href=\"https://kampkomiteen.net/?p=6938\">\n    here\n   </a>\n   .\n  </em>\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-gallery aligncenter has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-3 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9566\" data-id=\"9566\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"576\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Trondheim_1.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Trondheim_1.webp\" width=\"768\"/>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9567\" data-id=\"9567\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"576\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Trondheim_2.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Trondheim_2.webp\" width=\"768\"/>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9568\" data-id=\"9568\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"594\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Trondheim_3.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Trondheim_3.webp\" width=\"768\"/>\n  </figure>\n  <figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-caption wp-element-caption\">\n   <em>\n    Posters mobilizing for the 8\n    <sup>\n     th\n    </sup>\n    of March in Saupstad, south of Trondheim, Norway. Source: Kampkomiteen\n   </em>\n  </figcaption>\n </figure>\n <div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n  <figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9569\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1000\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Trondheim_7.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Trondheim_7.webp\" width=\"750\"/>\n   <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">\n    <em>\n     Posters mobilizing for the 8\n     <sup>\n      th\n     </sup>\n     of March in Heimdal, south of Trondheim, Norway. Source: Kampkomiteen\n    </em>\n   </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n </div>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-gallery aligncenter has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-4 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9570\" data-id=\"9570\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"682\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Trondheim_8-1024x682.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Trondheim_8-1024x682.webp\" width=\"1024\"/>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9571\" data-id=\"9571\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"682\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Trondheim_9-1024x682.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Trondheim_9-1024x682.webp\" width=\"1024\"/>\n  </figur