n    Of March in tampere, Finland. Source: Punalippu\n   </em>\n  </figcaption>\n </figure>\n</div>\n", "source": "https://redherald.org/2024/03/06/actions-and-statements-for-the-8th-of-march/", "type": "article", "title": "Actions and Statements for the 8th of March \u2013 The Red Herald", "description": "We share an overview of actions and statements that we have seen for the 8th March this year.", "modified time": "2024-03-06T21:54:38+00:00", "author": ["T.I."], "categories": ["Featured", "International"], "tags": ["8th of March"], "sections": ["Featured", "International", "8th of March", "English", "pll_65e8e67b87767"]}